## 2 Pts soln.

x→x(x-x0);x0∈[-2,2]

```julia
Plots.plot!(theme_dark(),xlim = (-3,3),ylim = (-5,5))
anm = @animate for x0 in -2:.05:2
    Plots.plot!(x-> x*(x-x0))
    Plots.title!("x-> x*(x-x0)")
end
#savefig(anm,doc_dir*"/quadxIntercepts.png")
```

```julia
#test
